item.title: NNDial Notes - 1
item.description: This is the Part 1 of notes for understanding NNDIAL which is a Network-based End-to-End Trainable Task-oriented Dialogue System developed by the Cambridge Dialogue System Group. This part focuses on the general structure of NNDIAL System.
